snippet.title: Every Journey - SWORD: DOTV TEASER TRAILER 2
snippet.description:
Every journey begins somewhere.

The Sword Team and WorthyWorm proudly presents a new game to come (and it's our first!), Sword: Depths of the Void. Explore a forgotten world and fight for your destiny against the V01??D. Coming soon in 2024 - 2025.

Subscribe for more info on this game.
